Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.26,0:00:34.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:34.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.88,0:00:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:49.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1179.518,406)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.19,0:00:56.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上周  一集前所未见的海绵宝宝剧集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:55.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Last week a never-before-seen episode
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:56.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:59.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(762,540)}尼克罗顿
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.76,0:01:00.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在尼克罗顿工作室桌底下被人发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:01:00.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was discovered under a desk at Nickelodeon Studios
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.24,0:01:04.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在全世界都在热切期待观看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:01.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now all the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:04.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is waiting in fevered anticipation to watch
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.48,0:01:08.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  失踪的剧集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:08.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the SpongeBob SquarePants "Lost Episode"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.30,0:01:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  即将播出失踪的剧集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, to present the lost episode
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.77,0:01:12.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要来到加州恩斯诺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:12.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from Encino, California
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.78,0:01:16.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有请海绵宝宝粉丝俱乐部的主席
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:16.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the president of the SpongeBob SquarePants Fan Club
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.00,0:01:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海盗派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patchy the Pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.02,0:01:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派斯  派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patchy, Patchy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.82,0:01:21.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孩子们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:21.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the kids are here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.49,0:01:24.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:24.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  你就不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty, don't you know
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.17,0:01:29.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派斯现在有私事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:29.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is Patchy's private time?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.56,0:01:31.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:31.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们来干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.78,0:01:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们是来看失踪的剧集的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're here to see the lost episode
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.36,0:01:38.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我没有失踪的剧集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:38.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I haven't got the lost episode
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.28,0:01:39.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:39.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.70,0:01:40.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给弄丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:40.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well, I lost it
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.99,0:01:42.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  派斯拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:42.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patchy, please
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.46,0:01:43.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别那么说  派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:43.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Patchy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.84,0:01:45.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是真丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:45.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it is
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.05,0:01:47.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它失踪了  我不知道它哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:47.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's lost, and I have no idea where it is
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.64,0:01:51.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们还是把海绵宝宝给忘掉得了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:51.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so it's best if you forget all about old SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:55.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,844)}怀念海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我居然会丢掉失踪的剧集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't believe I lost "The Lost Episode"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.20,0:02:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没丢过任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never lose anything
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你腿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about your leg?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.20,0:02:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.72,0:02:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一只眼睛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And your eye
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.67,0:02:49.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,眼睛丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:49.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the eye
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.31,0:02:50.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一只手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:50.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And your hand
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.57,0:02:55.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我滚出去  你个臭鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:55.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of here, you blasted bird
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.97,0:02:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是能有地图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only I had a map
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,指引我找到失踪的剧集就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to tell me where the lost episode is
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是张地图
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a map
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.50,0:03:09.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能带我找到我丢的海绵宝宝失踪剧集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:09.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a map to the lost episode of SpongeBob I lost
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934,272)}通向失踪剧集的地图
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美梦要成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a dream come true
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要去找到它  波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got to go find it, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.54,0:03:20.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过得先装上我的寻宝腿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:20.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, I'll need me treasure-hunting leg
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂快来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间不等人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time's a-wastin'
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在约翰逊太太家往前走十步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ten paces past Mrs. Johnson's house
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要不要吃饼干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you boys like some cookies?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先打包起来  约翰逊太太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put them in a doggie bag, Mrs. Johnson
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.22,0:03:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在没空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't right now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.01,0:03:37.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要寻宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:37.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're on a treasure hunt
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.93,0:03:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  别着凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, don't catch cold
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(688,346)}唐恩市场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:44.80,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 英寻：海洋测量中的深度单位，约合1.829米 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.40,0:03:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在唐恩进口货品及熟食店往前五英寻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:41.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Walk five fathoms
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,past Don's Import Store & Delicatessen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(592,294)}唐恩进口货品及熟食店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(410,814)}分叉树
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.65,0:03:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往分叉树走半里格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Half a league to the forked tree
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:48.50,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 里格：长度单位，用于航海，约合3.18海里 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.95,0:03:54.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就只剩下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:54.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now all that's left is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(468,532)}猴子湖之\N七大试炼
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猴子湖之七大试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The seven trials of Monkey Lagoon?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.18,0:04:05.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王保佑  都是为了海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:05.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merciful Neptune, only for SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是为了海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only for SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We made it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功挺过试炼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We survived the trials
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.55,0:04:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上就能挖到失踪的剧集了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm really going to dig this lost episode
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挖到  懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dig it, get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(618,920)}懂 吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.90,0:04:45.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你讲得好烂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:45.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You stink
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:45.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(852,920)}臭
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚洗过澡  才不臭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I just got out of the shower
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.17,0:04:50.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  我好像挖到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:50.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Potty, I think I hit something
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clever--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.10,0:04:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把财宝埋在地面上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bury your treasure above the surface
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.06,0:04:57.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:57.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也不知道这什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it means either
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.21,0:05:04.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过该找的都找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:04.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I got what I came for
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂快来  时间不等人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Potty, time's a-wastin'
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.23,0:05:11.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:11.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爆米花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Popcorn
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,soda
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腌大蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pickled garlic
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  赶紧按遥控器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Potty, hit the remote
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:22.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(514,568)}播放
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会特好看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to be great
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,348)}海绵宝宝  失踪的剧集
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.66,0:05:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又有海绵宝宝看了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,more SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太激动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is so exciting
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.61,0:05:35.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:35.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it comes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.39,0:05:37.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:37.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pipe down
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.82,0:06:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,失踪的剧集就这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's "The Lost Episode"?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是一堆便宜的循环走路动画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was just a bunch of cheap walk cycles
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.48,0:07:01.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太亏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:01.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a rip
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝背叛了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob betrayed us
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.76,0:07:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.60,0:07:13.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打一开始办了这家破粉丝俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:13.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ever started this stupid fan club in the first place
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.99,0:07:19.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把我的海绵宝宝周边全扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:19.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get rid of all my SpongeBob stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.90,0:07:20.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:20.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All of it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All of it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.72,0:07:26.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:26.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All of it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要跑路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to run away
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.10,0:07:28.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:28.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what I'll do--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,run away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:38.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(624,582)}海绵宝宝第{\fnArial}118{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}集\N真正的失踪剧集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:38.85,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 实为第59集 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  真是性急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jeez, what a hothead
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在播出真正的失踪剧集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now the real lost episode
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.45,0:07:38.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派斯  回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:38.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patchy, come back--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.36,0:07:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's more
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.52,0:07:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's watch
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.70,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(397,395)}会飞的\N{\fs30} \N{\fs150}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.23\pos(320.659,419.714)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.23\pos(644.659,713.714)}循环走路动画导演
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:58.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.23\pos(296.659,477.714)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.72\pos(380.659,299.714)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.1\pos(248.659,393.714)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.1\pos(492.659,725.714)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(744,718)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.11,0:08:05.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里有一位得意的水母捕手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:05.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we see the proud jellyfish hunter
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他一动不动地站着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He stands motionless
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.30,0:08:11.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诱骗水母  让它们误以为自己很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:11.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to lure the jellyfish into a false sense of security
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待到猎物一靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and when his prey ventures too close
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他便立刻行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he springs into action
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.15,0:08:39.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我向你致敬  宏伟的水母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:39.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I salute you, old majestic jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.30,0:08:42.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你对天空的驾驭能力无人能及
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:42.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your command of the sky is unmatched
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飘浮在我的水母网所不能及之处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,floating just out of the reach of my net
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.85,0:08:45.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,却又近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:45.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but near enough
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,足以让我欣赏你桀骜不驯的美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I can see your untamed beauty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.20,0:08:57.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但愿我能与你们共同飞上天去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:57.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only I could join you there in the air
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.00,0:09:00.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自在飘浮  无忧无虑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:09:00.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Floating free without a care
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望我能飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I could fly
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.20,0:09:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俯瞰一切  转变我的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And see things with a different eye
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.35,0:09:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以飞  扶摇万里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would fly so very high
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.76,0:09:13.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,触摸天空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:13.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and touch the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.11,0:09:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且不必过问为什么我不会飞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And never have to ask why it is that I can't fly
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.72,0:09:23.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点忘了海绵爷爷给我的教诲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:23.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm forgetting the words of Grandpa SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假如我们注定会飞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we were meant to fly
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.65,0:09:27.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么头上就得有螺旋桨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:27.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'd have propellers on our heads
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,背上就得有喷气引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or jet engines on our backs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.87,0:09:33.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要遵从他的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:33.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to follow his advice, by gum
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.15,0:09:34.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要发明一个飞天机器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:34.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll invent a flying machine
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么装置  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that contraption, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  那是飞天机器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That, Patrick, is a flying machine
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑什么笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.52,0:09:49.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就像是我爷爷曾经常说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:49.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's like my grandpa used to say
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.27,0:09:50.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假如我们注定会飞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:50.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we were meant to fly
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又不是你爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not your grandfather
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.43,0:09:56.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我要飞了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:56.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here I go, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要跟水母一起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm off to fly with the jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.94,0:09:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点火开关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:09:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ignition
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.75,0:10:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起落架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Landing gear
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.10,0:10:03.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:03.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费花生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Complimentary peanuts
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.67,0:10:06.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正常得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:06.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Checkaroo
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备起飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready for takeoff
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.28,0:10:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把简金斯农夫的粮仓切了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You cut a hole in Farmer Jenkins' grain silo
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.55,0:10:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别提醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't remind me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.85,0:10:24.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,城里人跟他们的飞天机器果然没好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:22.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew no good would come from
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,city folk and their flying machines
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.92,0:10:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.44,0:10:27.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:27.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们最好照他说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we better do what he says
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.22,0:10:31.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会种粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:31.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He knows how to grow food
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.10,0:10:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然花了一整个晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it took me all night
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.87,0:10:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but here they are--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.77,0:10:37.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新蓝图
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:37.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the new blueprints
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟上次那个可不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wasn't even close with that last one--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.41,0:10:41.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还螺旋桨  方向舵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,propellers, rudders
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次绝对飞得起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one's going to fly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can feel it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了没  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.71,0:10:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's working, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm flying
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.50,0:10:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,falling
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,物理学都研究明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The physics are all here
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次我一定飞得起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This time, I'm going to fly
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  要开生日派对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, a birthday party
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.37,0:11:13.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:13.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.62,0:11:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是海绵飞天机三型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is the SquarePants Flyer Mark III
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要挪开砖头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you do is remove the brick--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.09,0:11:19.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者说压舱物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:19.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or ballast--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.37,0:11:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是另起炉灶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, back to the drawing board
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在能吃蛋糕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we have the cake now?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy, happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.47,0:11:32.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好大开眼界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:32.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, get ready to say, "Eureka"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.28,0:11:34.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:34.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.05,0:11:35.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:35.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.60,0:11:37.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:37.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's working
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm flying
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.54,0:11:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看那个绑着风筝的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at that guy tied to a kite
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他干嘛那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is he doing that?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用怕  被束缚在地面的居民们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do not be afraid, Earthbound people
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我并不是只飞天怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not a flying monster
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而是你们的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am just one of you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.26,0:11:56.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:56.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.36,0:11:57.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:57.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.21,0:11:58.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:58.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.84,0:11:59.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:11:59.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(858,212)}便宜货超市
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.52,0:12:02.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:02.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(532,214)}快件
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.56,0:12:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想归还这个风筝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'd like to return this kite
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认得你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.15,0:12:08.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  今天的报纸上有报道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:08.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, from today's paper
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,742)}裤头村新闻\N本地疯子欲飞行
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本地疯子欲飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Local nutcase tries to fly"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我追个梦就成疯子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a nutcase because I follow my dreams?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.65,0:12:17.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正发明了电灯泡的那位也饱受嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, they laughed at the guy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who invented light bulbs, too
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.46,0:12:18.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:18.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, they didn't
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.78,0:12:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll see
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.06,0:12:23.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是裤头村鸟人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's the Birdman of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道他干嘛还用腿走路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder why he's still using his legs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  鸟人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Birdman
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.97,0:12:33.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扇动翅膀飞起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:33.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flap your wings and fly
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.80,0:12:37.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鸟人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:37.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Birdman
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.10,0:12:39.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去看下你家鸟蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:39.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,going to check on your eggs?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.57,0:12:43.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计他还在找雕像拉屎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:43.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's looking for a statue to poop on
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go on and laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天的裤头村可真是可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it is a sad day in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.45,0:12:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竟敢嘲笑一位怀抱远大梦想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when a guy is ridiculed for having dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.21,0:12:58.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你以为就你一个身怀未竟的梦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:58.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think you're the only one with unfulfilled dreams?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.71,0:13:01.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来应该是个开音乐会的钢琴家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:01.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to be a concert pianist
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.16,0:13:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果后来我才发现我没手指
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until I realized I didn't have any fingers
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都有过梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We all had dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你凭什么觉得自己了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What makes you so special?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get him
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚越远越好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good riddance
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.20,0:13:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大梦想家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,dreamer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(690,876)}清淤
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.45,0:13:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少不会变得更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it can't get any worse
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(696,918)}羽毛运送
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我话讲早了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I spoke too soon
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.67,0:13:31.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝还能学会飞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:31.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will SpongeBob learn to fly?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.51,0:13:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要走开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay tuned
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母们又飞走了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There they go again, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.87,0:13:41.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来没法跟水母一起畅游空中了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll never join them in the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能困在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be stuck on the ground
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一辈子无法飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sentenced to a flightless life
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.51,0:13:48.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  看来一切梦想注定无法实现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:48.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I guess all dreams aren't meant to come true
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.71,0:13:50.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回归现实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:50.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to reality
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.72,0:13:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.47,0:13:54.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的梦想很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:54.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my dreams are silly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(858,272)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.52,0:14:01.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:01.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.84,0:14:04.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我不是裤头村鸟人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:04.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't the Birdman of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.79,0:14:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.69,0:14:08.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我才没住鸟笼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:08.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I certainly do not live in a birdcage
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倪娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Joe Mama"?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我听好  姓倪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, listen up, Joe
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.77,0:14:15.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就直说了  飞行根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:15.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate to break it to you, but flying is impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我得挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to go now
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,头刚撞天花板上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My head just hit the ceiling
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.22,0:14:21.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:21.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.10,0:14:21.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:21.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'm flying
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母田  我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish Fields, here I come
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.63,0:14:27.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:27.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom, look
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.64,0:14:29.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那个飞人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:29.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the flying guy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来他到头来不是个疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess he wasn't a lunatic after all
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm flying
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在飞翔  他在飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's flying, he's flying
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他真的真的在飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's really, really flying
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,群众笑  过客嘲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They laughed, they scoffed
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当时我无法飞云霄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before I had liftoff
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.10,0:14:44.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但他正在飞翔  在空中飞得高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:44.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But now he's flying, he's flying high in the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.10,0:14:47.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我很想留一句  我早说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:47.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love to hang around to say "I told you so"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.23,0:14:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是前往水母田才适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's off to Jellyfish Fields I go
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,604)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不愿意走大马路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roads and streets are not for me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.33,0:14:53.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:53.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.86,0:14:54.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:54.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please help
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的蜗牛困上了树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My snail is up a tree
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.62,0:15:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从小就一直在养着它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:15:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had her since I was a little girl
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.28,0:15:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但看样子它将命丧黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But now it looks like the end of her world
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.15,0:15:11.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:11.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下次试试坐电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next time, try the elevator
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  鸟人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Birdman
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.15,0:15:24.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从未感到这么自在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:24.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have never felt so free
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.25,0:15:27.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万里长空是我热衷的地带
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:27.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,High in the sky is the place for me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.52,0:15:31.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,云端之上为朋友出手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:31.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Helping friends from up above
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.25,0:15:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我的深深爱慕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are the things that I love
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.57,0:15:37.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会帮蟹老板取回他的硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:37.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll help Mr. Krabs reclaim his dime
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.50,0:15:39.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发财了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:39.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm rich
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.65,0:15:45.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拯救派大星  逃离这出哑剧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:45.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll save Patrick from this mime
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.97,0:15:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.37,0:15:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就连痞老板也需要帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even Plankton needs some help
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.47,0:15:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,此时此刻他被海草缠住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When he gets tangled in the kelp
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麻烦你放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please put me down
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:07.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,588)}裤头村新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.33,0:16:03.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村的大众正广泛热议
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:03.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All of Bikini Bottom is abuzz over
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.68,0:16:07.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一位神秘飞人帮手的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:06.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the identity of a mysterious flying man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who helps people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(328,900)}新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.22,0:16:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他找到了我的假发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He found my hairpiece
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会帮大家忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He helps people
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.69,0:16:15.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还会飞  还会帮大家忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:15.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he flies and he helps people
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.20,0:16:17.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁知道他还会用什么英勇之举
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:17.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who knows what superhero act of courage
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.73,0:16:19.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,震撼到我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:19.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he'll astound us with next?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.57,0:16:25.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好  酷乐湖灯塔的灯灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:25.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, the light in the Goo Lagoon lighthouse went out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.62,0:16:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简金斯水手要开上海岸线了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sailor Jenkins is headed for the coastline
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.50,0:16:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不种田了我可真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I gave up farming
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  神秘的飞人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, mysterious flying man
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.73,0:16:50.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,城里人跟他们的飞天机器果然没好事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:47.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew no good would come from
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,city folk and their flying machines
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.74,0:16:53.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一天的好事也做得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:53.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's enough good deeds for one day
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟水母们还有一场约会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a date with a flock of jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.38,0:16:56.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:56.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, son
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要你跟你的神奇裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need you and your magical pants
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.15,0:17:01.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板  我发明这裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:01.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs, I invented these pants
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是要跟水母一起飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I could fly with the jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我一直帮大家忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I keep doing favors for people
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的梦想就没办法成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never get to make my dreams a reality
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是海绵宝宝  这次情况特别紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, SpongeBob, it's an emergency
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.37,0:17:13.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:13.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's roll
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去哪  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where to, Mr. K?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.58,0:17:16.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的船库
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:16.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My garage
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么紧急情况  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the emergency, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定准备好了吗  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure you're up for it, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的裤子多半能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think my pants can handle it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to clean
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扫除犯罪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clean up crime?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的船库
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my garage
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你紧急情况就那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's your emergency?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是海绵宝宝  众所周知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, SpongeBob, everyone knows
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞起来就更方便扫船库了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's easier to clean a garage when you can fly
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.07,0:17:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就扫你的船库
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll clean your garage
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后就别来找我帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But after this, no more favors
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完成  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All done, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可回收垃圾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the recyclables?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.60,0:17:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aw, shrimp
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.04,0:17:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母田  我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish Fields, here I come
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.82,0:17:53.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:53.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星有麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's in trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.13,0:17:55.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:55.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.96,0:17:56.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:56.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能帮我挠肚皮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you scratch my tummy?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.32,0:18:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能帮我挑领带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help me pick out a tie?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能清理我浴缸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clean my bathtub?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.05,0:18:08.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能结算我的账目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:08.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Balance my checkbook?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.73,0:18:11.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能帮忙散播邪恶话语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:11.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help spread the word of evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:12.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(896,902)}邪恶
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能解开我电话线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Untangle my phone cord?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能做我几何作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do my geometry?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能跟我植物对话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Talk to my plants?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.15,0:18:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能搓我头皮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rub my scalp?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.22,0:18:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.60,0:18:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.37,0:18:23.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:23.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.42,0:18:26.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在应该是在水母田里才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:26.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to be at Jellyfish Fields right now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.52,0:18:28.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果我却是在搓你头皮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:28.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but instead I'm rubbing your scalp
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更何况我根本就不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I don't even know who you are
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们是小学同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we went to elementary school together
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.40,0:18:34.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丹尼斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:34.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dennis?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.37,0:18:36.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:36.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.47,0:18:42.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:42.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.14,0:18:45.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是甩不掉那群占便宜的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:45.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I don't give these feverish favor-seekers the slip
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.46,0:18:47.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就没法跟水母一起飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:47.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never get to fly with the jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.72,0:18:50.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:50.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There he is
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's getting away
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他还有忙没帮到我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, he owes us favors
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get him
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.37,0:19:16.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就快到水母田了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:16.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm almost at Jellyfish Fields
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.34,0:19:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他往水母田飞过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's headed for Jellyfish Fields
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下抓不到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll never catch him now
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of this
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:27.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(654,640)}炮弹简金斯
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.72,0:19:26.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是炮弹简金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:26.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Cannonball Jenkins
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.57,0:19:37.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,城里人跟他们的飞天机器准没好事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nothing good would come from
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,city folk and their flying machines
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.14,0:19:45.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:45.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have we done?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要好好安葬他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think a proper burial is in order
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.56,0:19:55.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种裤子一辈子只会出现一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:53.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pair of pants like these
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come around once in a lifetime
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.87,0:20:02.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好时光不长久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:02.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it was fun while it lasted
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到头来我注定没办法飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm not meant to fly after all
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.29,0:20:13.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的水母朋友在帮我飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:13.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My jellyfish friends are helping me fly
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.97,0:20:15.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还不用裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:15.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without pants
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.56,0:20:18.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来这一切的道理都是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:18.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess it just goes to show
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.82,0:20:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞行不需要飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't need a plane to fly
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.67,0:20:26.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,塑料翅膀会让你哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:26.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plastic wings may make you cry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.37,0:20:30.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,风筝只有起风才能用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:30.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kites are made for windy days
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.47,0:20:34.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,气球躺椅容易飞离
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:34.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lawn chair with balloons fly away
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.24,0:20:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,充气的裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Inflatable pants
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.13,0:20:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从此可以告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may as well skip
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.60,0:20:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果想要飞  需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want to fly, all you need
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.77,0:20:48.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是友谊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:48.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is friendship
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  水母们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, jellies
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.73,0:20:57.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们教会了我宝贵的一课
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:57.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You taught me a valuable lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.07,0:20:59.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然不太确定这一课是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:59.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Although I'm not quite sure what it was
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.42,0:21:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起飞到匹萨店买片匹萨吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's fly down to the pizza house for a slice
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.17,0:21:04.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会再飞了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:04.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more flying for me, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母能自在飞行就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll leave that to the jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道派大星刚刚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did Patrick just
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.11,0:21:14.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:14.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.32,0:21:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很好看啊  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that great, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再看一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's watch it again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这提议不错  波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.58,0:21:27.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遥控器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:27.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the remote?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.01,0:21:28.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遥控器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:28.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the remote?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.44,0:21:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我遥控器丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost the remote
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.97,0:21:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种东西就应该做得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They should make those things
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.27,0:21:39.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的遥控器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:39.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My remote
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.80,0:21:41.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:41.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, stranger
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.69,0:21:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不客气  派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it, Patchy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.25,0:21:46.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:46.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.47,0:21:50.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪颗破按钮才是倒带按钮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:50.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which one of these cockamamie buttons is "Rewind"?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.15,0:21:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这颗不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.02,0:21:55.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wrong again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.90,0:21:59.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来按
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:21:59.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me do it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.87,0:22:00.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:00.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.85,0:22:02.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是电灯开关
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:02.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the light switch
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.92,0:22:09.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是墨西哥街头乐队按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:09.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the "Mariachi Band" button
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.37,0:22:13.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨高科技
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:13.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate technology
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒带啊  破东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rewind, darn you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.22,0:22:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.22,0:22:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Failure ahoy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.84,0:22:27.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  停
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:27.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.49,0:22:29.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:29.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stop
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.97,0:22:30.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:30.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.63,0:22:32.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破铜烂铁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:32.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,infernal machine
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.91,0:22:37.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了  我把失踪的剧集毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:37.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I've ruined the lost episode
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.34,0:22:40.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下它永远消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:40.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's lost forever
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.10,0:22:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lost forever
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.00,0:22:43.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  真是个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:43.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, what a loser
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.22,0:22:47.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来失踪的剧集会一直消失下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:47.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess the lost episode will remain lost
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.42,0:22:49.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但无论有没有带子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:49.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But tape or no tape
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.07,0:22:51.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要天上还有星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:51.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as long as there are stars in the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.46,0:22:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝会永远活在我们的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob will live on in our hearts and in our minds
